    "description": "Download Lotus Chess Here! https://onelink.to/lotus-agadmator \nSearch all my videos easy https://agadmator-library.github.io/\n\nIvanchuk, Vasyl (2630) - Dubov, Daniil (2686)\nFIDE World Rapid Championship 2025 (Chess.com) [10] 2025.12.28\nD31 Queen's Gambit Declined, semi-Slav, Koomen variation\n\n1.Nf3 d5 2.g3 c5 3.Bg2 Nf6 4.O-O g6 5.c4 Bg7 6.d4 cxd4 7.Nxd4 O-O 8.cxd5 Nxd5 9.Nb3 Nb4 10.Nc3 N8c6 11.Bf4 Bf5 12.a3 Na6 13.Rc1 Rc8 14.Na4 Qe8 15.e4 Be6 16.Nbc5 Rd8 17.Qe1 Nd4 18.Kh1 b6 19.Nxa6 Qxa4 20.Nb4 Bg4 21.Nd5 Be2 22.Nxe7+ Kh8 23.Rg1 Qb5 24.Qb4 Qxb4 25.axb4 Nf3 26.Nc6 Rc8 27.Nxa7 Ra8 28.Rc7 Nxg1 29.Kxg1 g5 30.Bd6 Rad8 31.e5 Bxe5 32.Bxe5+ f6 33.Be4 Rd1+ 34.Kg2 fxe5 35.f3 g4 36.f4 Bf3+ 37.Bxf3 Rd2+ 38.Kf1 gxf3 39.fxe5 Rxh2 40.e6 f2 41.Rf7 Rxf7 42.exf7 Kg7 43.Nc8 Rh6 44.Kxf2 Kxf7 45.Kf3 Rc6 46.Na7 Rc4 47.b5 Ke6 48.Nc6 h5 49.b3 Rg4 50.b4 Kd6 51.Kf2 Kd5 52.Kf3 Rg7 53.Kf4\n\n0:01 Hello Everyone!\n00:50 Game Starts!\n02:50 Completely New Game!\n05:50 Pause the Video!\n08:00 It Was in This Position!\n08:15 Let's Have some Fun!\n10:55 Legends of The Channel\n\nCheck out agadmator's merch here https://teespring.com/stores/agadmators-swag-store\nhttps://teespring.com/design-with-a-story-tm\n\nMailbox where you can send stuff:\n\nAntonio Radić\nAGADMATOR d.o.o.\nFranje Tuđmana 12\nCroatia\n48260 Križevci \np.s. this is not my home address :)\n\nContact me: agadmator@gmail.com \n\nVideo created by OBS\n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\nIf you realllly enjoy my content, you're welcome to support me and my channel with a small donation via PayPal or Crypto.\n\nLink to PayPal donation https://www.paypal.me/agadmator\n\nMaiar Wallet @agadmator or join me here https://get.maiar.com/referral/pv0mam6l2a\nBTC address bc1qckd3ut0hqyymzv33eus97ld8klj02xhk2kcwld\nBCH address qzmfclyn69hqhjslls40r7r0dsttwe3tcsl946w4fr\nLTC address Laarf1RmvCpLt2BcSwC1PBLG3hRC4HjBrz